300 1255 M
(complexity without real benefits, and that much the same effect could be)t
300 1295 M
(obtained by users via specific namespace-declarations.)t
300 1375 M
(Since that time the library has grown more complex. Several committee members)t
300 1415 M
(feel that reintroducing sub-namespaces would result in a cleaner design for)t
300 1455 M
(the library.)t
300 1535 M
