450 455 M
(What does \223extend\224 mean in 17.3.3.1?)t
450 535 M
(Nathan Myers discusses the issues in message c++std-lib-4366:)t
450 615 M
(In Tokyo we discussed the issue of what entities could be)t
450 655 M
(added by users to the "std" namespace.  This is a little bit)t
450 695 M
(misleading, because users are not allowed to add names, or)t
450 735 M
(overload existing names, and we should be clear about that.)t
450 815 M
(The issue is really about templates can be specialized in the)t
450 855 M
(std namespace.  This is necessary in some cases because the)t
450 895 M
(user of the specialization cannot be expected to know that)t
450 935 M
(the type is specialized.  In other cases it would be a)t
450 975 M
(substantial convenience.)t
450 1055 M
(Here are a few I \(or others\) have identified:)t
450 1135 M
(  In Clause 25, all the algorithms must occasionally be specialized)t
450 1175 M
(for certain data structures \(or rather, their )t
1508 1175 M
(iterators\).)t
450 1215 M
(In Clause 18, the )t
864 1215 M
(numeric_limits template must routinely be)t
450 1255 M
(specialized for user types.  Each of the containers in clauses)t
450 1295 M
(21 and 23 must be specialized for certain user )t
1531 1295 M
(allocators.)t
450 1335 M
(Some of the )t
726 1335 M
(iterator )t
933 1335 M
(adaptors \(e.g. insert\) in Clause 24 must)t
450 1375 M
(be \(partial-\) specialized for certain data structures.  The)t
450 1415 M
(traits template in Clause 27 must be specialized if users are)t
450 1455 M
(to benefit by the default traits parameter on stream templates.)t
450 1535 M
(This list has got quite long, and my confidence in our ability)t
450 1575 M
(to generate an exhaustive and correct list flags.  I would like)t
450 1615 M
(to propose instead that )t
1002 1615 M
(specializations of any standard template)t
450 1655 M
(on any *user-defined type* are permitted.  Then it becomes the)t
450 1695 M
(responsibility of the definer of that type to ensure that any)t
450 1735 M
(specializations implement the semantics described in the standard.)t
300 1815 M
(Resolution:)t
300 1895 M
(Modify 17.3.3.1 [)t
691 1895 M
(lib.reserved.names] to read:)t
450 1975 M
(A C++ program shall not add declarations or definitions to namespace)t
450 2015 M
(std unless otherwise specified.  A program may add template)t
450 2055 M
