(annexes.)t
300 836 M
(Resolution:)t
450 916 M
(Take no action.)t
450 996 M
(The current separation of the library into several clauses provides)t
450 1036 M
(coherent organization.  Moving some material to normative annexes would)t
450 1076 M
(confuse the presentation.  The document is intended to be an ANSI/ISO)t
450 1116 M
(Standard conforming to IEC/ISO Directives - Part 3, Drafting and)t
450 1156 M
(presentation.  It is not intended to be a reference manual.)t
