450 295 M
(The choice of classes and functions for the standard library involves)t
450 335 M
(complex tradeoffs between a desire to keep the library small and)t
450 375 M
(tractable, the need to provide a base set of functionality facilitating)t
450 415 M
(communication between third-party libraries, and many other factors.)t
450 495 M
(The current library provides a set of classes and functions which has)t
450 535 M
(evolved over five years of detailed discussions, and the committee is)t
450 575 M
(satisfied that an acceptable balance has been struck between the)t
450 615 M
(competing needs.)t
