(    provided but not within the namespace scope of the namespace std.)t
300 575 M
(4.  Section D.4 \(Standard C library headers\) paragraph 2 states:)t
300 655 M
(    Each C header, whose name has the form )t
1289 655 M
(name.h includes its)t
300 695 M
(    corresponding C++ header )t
967 695 M
(cname, followed by an explicit using-declaration)t
300 735 M
