300 935 M
(    Each C header, whose name has the form )t
1289 935 M
(name.h behaves as if)t
300 975 M
(    each name placed in the Standard library namespace by the corresponding)t
300 1015 M
(    )t
392 1015 M
(cname header is also placed within the namespace scope of the)t
300 1055 M
(    namespace std and is followed by an explicit using-declaration \(7.3.3\).)t
300 1135 M
(    Rationale:)t
300 1215 M
(    This wording specifies the intent of the <)t
1358 1215 M
(name.h> headers without)t
300 1255 M
(    specifying the implementation.  It allows C++ Standard library vendors)t
300 1295 M
(    to supply the <)t
737 1295 M
(name.h> headers listed in D.4 in the way that is)t
300 1335 M
(    most appropriate to their users.)t
